name: My Lovely Kaye
wishText: i just want you to know that you make me feel like i matter. you make me feel seen and heard. i just wanted to tell you how much i appreciate you for that. i appreciate everything that you do. i'am always proud of you. i will always be here for you, supporting you. no matter what happens just remember i'll always love you through anything and everything. i will always be thankful for you. thank you for being so thoughtful and caring. thank you for listening to me and understanding me. thank you for just being there. above all thank you for accepting me and choosing to love me each and everyday. I Love You Always My Princess!
